Package tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.UIModels

Class Sphere

java.lang.Object
tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.UIModels.Sphere
public class Sphere
extends java.lang.Object
Sphere is a class which contains all the size and movement specifications for the sphere to operate within the game, as well as initializing the sphere itself.
